**Amendment**: Add worktree-safe grep pattern for ALREADY-DONE verification, correct pre-filter order (DUPLICATE → ALREADY-DONE → verify-before-fix → LOW), updated notes on `isolation="worktree"` reliability and agent git-op completion.

